PHASE 1: Normalized File Creation

01) Validate file/directory attributes
02) Create normalized file and write metadata header
03) Extract text from source file incrementally
04) Normalize extracted text incrementally
05) Write normalized text incrementally to normalized file
06) Finalize and close normalized file

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PHASE 2: Chunk Creation

01). Validate normalized file/directory attributes
02). Create chunk directory for the normalized file
03). Read normalized file incrementally (fixed-size reads)
04). Accumulate text in chunk buffer based on chunk strategy
05). Split buffer into semantic chunks when size/strategy condition is met
06). Create chunk file and write metadata header
07). Write chunk text to chunk file
08). Finalize and close chunk file
09). Repeat until entire normalized file is processed

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PHASE 3: Embedding Generation

01). Validate chunk file/directory attributes
02). Create embeddings directory for the chunk file
03). Read chunk file and extract metadata header
04). Read chunk text from chunk file
05). Prepare embedding request (attach metadata and model configuration)
06). Accumulate chunk requests into embedding batch
07). Generate embeddings using embedding model (batched)
08). Create embedding file and write metadata header
09). Write embedding vector and chunk metadata to embedding file
10). Finalize and close embedding file
11). Repeat until all chunk files are processed

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PHASE 4: Vector DB Storage

01). Validate embedding file/directory attributes
02). Initialize vector database connection and configuration
03). Read embedding file and extract metadata header
04). Read embedding vector and associated chunk metadata
05). Prepare vector DB record (id, vector, metadata, source information)
06). Accumulate embedding records into storage batch
07). Store embeddings in vector database (batched insert/upsert)
08). Capture vector DB response (vector id, status, errors if any)
09). Update embedding file with vector DB storage metadata (optional)
10). Finalize and close database transaction/batch
11). Repeat until all embedding files are processed

------------------------------- Query and Answer Generation PHASE ------------------------

01) Receive user query
02) Normalize / preprocess query
03) Generate embedding for query
04) Retrieve top-K relevant chunks
05) Assemble context from retrieved chunks
06) Build prompt (context + question)
07) Call LLM
08) Post-process LLM response
09) Return final answer (optionally with sources)

